Epidemiology
Source of the outbreak(s) or origin of infection: unknown or inconclusive

Control measures
Measures applied: movement control inside the country, screening, disinfection/disinfestations, quarantine, zoning; stamping out; no treatment of affected animals;

Vaccination in response to the outbreak(s):
